Confidential: For Candidate Evaluation Only

This repository is a take-home coding exercise provided by Herbalife for the
sole purpose of evaluating a candidate's work. It is confidential and is shared
only with the candidate and the Herbalife hiring team.

Do not redistribute, publish, or share this repository or your solution
publicly (including on public source-code hosting). Please keep your submission
private and return it only to your Herbalife recruiter.
